    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/14290/" target="_blank">【人文与社会】译丛——译林出版社</a>
                <span class="pl">(彼岸)</span>
